547
00:36:13,800 --> 00:36:15,633
Leave the radio alone.

548
00:36:17,400 --> 00:36:18,733
- It was modern.

549
00:36:18,733 --> 00:36:20,667
- Yeah, before it was
so goddamn modern,

550
00:36:20,667 --> 00:36:22,133
