554
00:36:43,567 --> 00:36:44,400
- Right.

555
00:36:53,033 --> 00:36:53,867
Is that it?

556
00:36:53,867 --> 00:36:54,700
- Yeah.

557
00:36:55,867 --> 00:36:58,300
- Then what are we doing
