583
00:38:08,133 --> 00:38:08,967
- Good.

584
00:38:12,733 --> 00:38:14,433
- I'll have a beer.

585
00:38:14,433 --> 00:38:15,267
- Thanks.

586
00:38:23,100 --> 00:38:25,833
(combative hits)

587
00:38:32,167 --> 00:38:34,500
-  C'mon man.

588
00:38:38,233 --> 00:38:39,900
