(suspenseful music)

603
00:39:58,167 --> 00:40:00,733
(pained moans)

604
00:40:01,867 --> 00:40:04,267
Game over, game over.

605
00:40:04,267 --> 00:40:05,833
(two gunshots)

606
00:40:05,833 --> 00:40:07,000
- Police.

