664
00:43:05,233 --> 00:43:06,300
- Hiding out?

665
00:43:06,300 --> 00:43:07,700
- No, no, no.

666
00:43:07,700 --> 00:43:10,167
About financing his
takeover in Japan.

667
00:43:10,167 --> 00:43:12,000
He's here to make money.

668
00:43:12,000 --> 00:43:13,467
I also found out
our friend Decklin

669
00:43:13,467 --> 00:43:15,267
