00:50:14,167 --> 00:50:15,600
Not Father Munoz.

770
00:50:16,733 --> 00:50:18,233
Oh God, thank you.

771
00:50:20,100 --> 00:50:21,933
- I want everybody strapped,

772
00:50:21,933 --> 00:50:24,367
I want every piece we've
